original: Boquist, Sven-Otto Leonard, notarie, Linköping, f. 16/9/13 i Kättilstad, östergötl. 1., av godsförv. Karl-Otto B. o. Signe-Maria Holstensson. G. 46 m. Birgittasyst. sjuksköt. Karin Peterson. — Stud:ex. 34, jur. kand. 44. Tjg. å landsfiskalskont., doms. o. länsstyr., tf. bitr. ’stadsombudsman i Linköp. fr. 47.
translated: Boquist, Sven-Otto Leonard, clerk, Linköping, b. September 16, 1913 in Kättilstad, Östergötland, son of estate manager Karl-Otto B. and Signe-Maria Holstensson. Married in 1946 to Karin Peterson, sister of a nurse. — Completed high school in 1934, graduated with a law degree in 1944. Employed at county police, courts, and county authority, acting deputy city attorney in Linköping from 1947.
